data.description: WOW! This splendid 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is ideally located near a scenic park and tranquil lake, offering a perfect blend of serenity and modern comfort. Elegant steel double front door with windows that you can open on a beautiful breezy day. This thoughtfully designed home boasts modern conveniences, including, FOAM INSULATION in the attic, a CENTRAL VACCUM SYSTEM for easy maintenance, a TANKLESS WATER HEATER for efficiency, and a robust SECURITY SYSTEM, including 3 monitors, for peace of mind. Elevate your living experience with the added comfort of a WATER SOFTENER and imagine the possibilities with the SURROUND SYSTEM in the front room. An exceptional floor layout featuring a designated office or theater space, formal dining area, and a primary room separated from the two additional bedrooms. Immerse yourself in a lifestyle of comfort and leisure, where every detail has been thoughtfully curated for your enjoyment. Mounted TVs, fridge, washer, and dryer are negotiable!
